McDonald’s Sells Stake In India Venture Hardcastle, Times Says

-- B y   P r a t i s h   N a r a y a n a n
-- 
2011-02-21T01:23:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/mcdonald-s-sells-stake-in-india-venture-hardcastle-times-says.html
  McDonald’s Corp . is selling its 50
percent stake in its Indian venture Hardcastle Restaurant Pvt.
Ltd., the Economic Times reported, citing Hardcastle Vice
Chairman Amit Jatia. McDonald’s is selling the stake to its
Indian joint venture partner, the BL Jatia family, for an
undisclosed amount, according to the newspaper.  Click here for web link  To contact the reporter on this story:
